#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:4
msgid "Installing Mattermost Server"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:6
msgid "Install Mattermost Server on a 64-bit machine."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:8
msgid "Assume that the IP address of this server is 10.10.10.2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:10
msgid "**To install Mattermost Server on RHEL 7**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:12
msgid ""
"Log in to the server that will host Mattermost Server and open a terminal"
" window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:14
msgid ""
"Download `the latest version of the Mattermost Server "
"<https://about.mattermost.com/download/>`__. In the following command, "
"replace ``X.X.X`` with the version that you want to download:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:16
msgid ""
"``wget https://releases.mattermost.com/X.X.X/mattermost-X.X.X-linux-"
"amd64.tar.gz``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:18
msgid "Extract the Mattermost Server files."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:20
msgid "``tar -xvzf *.gz``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:22
msgid "Move the extracted file to the ``/opt`` directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:24
msgid "``sudo mv mattermost /opt``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:26
msgid "Create the storage directory for files."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:28
msgid "``sudo mkdir /opt/mattermost/data``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:31
msgid ""
"The storage directory will contain all the files and images that your "
"users post to Mattermost, so you need to make sure that the drive is "
"large enough to hold the anticipated number of uploaded files and images."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:33
msgid ""
"Set up a system user and group called ``mattermost`` that will run this "
"service, and set the ownership and permissions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:35
msgid "``sudo useradd --system --user-group mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:36
msgid "``sudo chown -R mattermost:mattermost /opt/mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:37
msgid "``sudo chmod -R g+w /opt/mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:39
msgid ""
"Set up the database driver in the file "
"``/opt/mattermost/config/config.json``. Open the file as root in a text "
"editor and make the following changes:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:41
msgid "If you are using PostgreSQL:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:42
msgid "Set ``\"DriverName\"`` to ``\"postgres\"``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:43
msgid ""
"Set ``\"DataSource\"`` to the following value, replacing ``<mmuser-"
"password>`` and ``<host-name-or-IP>`` with the appropriate values:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:44
msgid ""
"``\"postgres://mmuser:<mmuser-password>@<host-name-or-"
"IP>:5432/mattermost?sslmode=disable&connect_timeout=10\"``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:45
msgid "If you are using MySQL:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:46
msgid "Set ``\"DriverName\"`` to ``\"mysql\"``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:47
msgid ""
"Set ``\"DataSource\"`` to the following value, replacing ``<mmuser-"
"password>`` and ``<host-name-or-IP>`` with the appropriate values. Also "
"make sure that the database name is ``mattermost`` instead of "
"``mattermost_test``:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:48
msgid ""
"``\"mmuser:<mmuser-password>@tcp(<host-name-or-"
"IP>:3306)/mattermost?charset=utf8mb4,utf8&readTimeout=30s&writeTimeout=30s\"``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:50
msgid ""
"Also set ``\"SiteURL\"`` to the full base URL of the site (e.g. "
"``\"https://mattermost.example.com\"``)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:52
msgid "Test the Mattermost server to make sure everything works."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:54
msgid "Change to the ``mattermost`` directory:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:55
msgid "``cd /opt/mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:56
msgid "Start the Mattermost server as the user mattermost:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:58
msgid "``sudo -u mattermost ./bin/mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:60
msgid ""
"When the server starts, it shows some log information and the text "
"``Server is listening on :8065``. You can stop the server by pressing "
"CTRL+C in the terminal window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:62
msgid "Set up Mattermost to use the systemd init daemon which handles"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:63
msgid "supervision of the Mattermost process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:65
msgid "Create the Mattermost configuration file:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:67
msgid "``sudo touch /etc/systemd/system/mattermost.service``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:69
msgid ""
"Open the configuration file in your favorite text editor, and copy the "
"following lines into the file:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:90
msgid ""
"If you are using MySQL, replace ``postgresql-9.4.service`` by "
"``mysqld.service`` in the ``[unit]`` section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:92
msgid "Make the service executable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:94
msgid "``sudo chmod 664 /etc/systemd/system/mattermost.service``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:96
msgid "Reload the systemd services."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:98
msgid "``sudo systemctl daemon-reload``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:100
msgid "Set Mattermost to start on boot."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:102
msgid "``sudo systemctl enable mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:104
msgid "Start the Mattermost server."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:106
msgid "``sudo systemctl start mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:108
msgid "Verify that Mattermost is running."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:110
msgid "``curl http://localhost:8065``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/install-rhel-7-mattermost.rst:112
msgid "You should see the HTML that's returned by the Mattermost server."
msgstr ""

